{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"72da5b5ad6","title":"第五部分 “四人帮”被粉碎后策划反革命武装叛乱，负隅顽抗进行垂死挣扎","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"edf9bd001e","index":0,"year":1977,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"72da5b5ad6"}],"tags":[{"id":"33b85cb7de","name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"88958321be","name":"云南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"cb691834e6","name":"王必成","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866","name":"黄兆其的部分罪行材料（1977.7）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"img","author":"朱、黄专案组","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/1.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/2.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/3.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/4.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/5.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/6.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/7.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/8.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/9.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/10.jp